title: Thảo Cầm Viên
about: There are a lot of animal in this place. It is suitable for having family meeting. I also love to drive hourse, fish massage, and petting panda.
address: Số 2 Đường Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm, Phường Bến Nghé, Quận 1, TP. HCM

title: Kart 1
about: A good place to go with friends. Racing is fun and exciting for youth. So if I have a chance, I would go here to compete with friends.
address: 582/12 Đường Huỳnh Tấn Phát, Phường Tân Phú, Quận 7, TP. HCM

title: Công viên Lê Thị Riêng
about: A good place to hangout with friends and lover. We brought snack, drinks there to celebreate my girlfriends birthday. It is good weather in the early morning, and late evening. Very suitable for relaxation.
address: 875 Đường Cách Mạng Tháng 8, Phường 15, Quận 10, TP. HCM

title: Zone 87
about: A good place to hangout with friends and lover. It has lots of restaurants near the area, and bar club. I visited here on vestial time which is very excited.
address: Số 87 Đường Nguyễn Huệ, Phường Bến Nghé, Quận 1, TP. HCM

title: Jump Arena
about: A good place to hangout with friends. It has lots of restaurants near the area. It is suitable if you want to do exercise and competiting with friends.
address: 60 Xa lộ Hà Nội, Phường Thảo Điền, Quận 2, TP. HCM

title: Chợ Bến Thành
about: A good place to hangout with friends, families, and lovers. It has lots of restaurants. It is suitable if you want to shopping unique items in Vietnam and enjoy the cuisine.
address: Đường Lê Lợi, thuộc phường Bến Nghé, Quận 1, TP. HCM

title: Vinhomes Central Park
about: A good place to hangout with friends, families, and lovers. It has lots of restaurants and shopping center near the place. It is suitable if you want to shopping and enjoy the cuisine. It is a little hot if you go in the summer.
address: Số 208 đường Nguyễn Hữu Cảnh, thuộc phường 22, quận Bình Thạnh, TP. HCM

title: Phố đi bộ Nguyễn Huệ
about: A good place to hangout with friends, families, and lovers. It has lots of restaurants, coffee shops, bookstore, and shopping center near the place. It is suitable if you want to shopping and enjoy the cuisine. It is a little hot if you go in the summer. It is also too crownded if you go on holiday.
address: Số 208 đường Nguyễn Hữu Cảnh, thuộc phường 22, quận Bình Thạnh, TP. HCM
